title: PolitiFact - Here's the readout of Donald Trump's call with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky
subtitle: The White House has released a declassified summary of a July 25 telephone call between President Donald Trump and Ukrai
author: www.politifact.com
vclaim: The White House has released a declassified summary of a July 25 telephone call between President Donald Trump and Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky. The leaders discussed reviving a dormant Ukrainian government investigation into a Ukrainian energy company that Joe Biden’s son, Hunter, served as a board member on while his father was vice president.
